issue.title: Topic info command line doesn't list subscribers

content.raw:
Hi, 
While I was working on this bug, I faced some difficulties while executing files.
When I 'make' files under the [src ](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/src/12e02afe310ca7330d11800ea5bf81272941ab4c/src/?at=ign-transport4)folder, I can see the executable file only under the 'ignition-transport5.dir' and the following error is being displayed when I try to execute it

'bash: ./Publisher.cc.o: cannot execute binary file: Exec format error'

Is there something that I am missing out on after successfully making files ?
